{"tid":1385622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5號全民罷工集會分析","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:31:58.000Z","uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0bc5fb86613dd4bc19dccbaca7d1ff9834d89c","tid":1385622,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"八月五號會有全民大罷工同埋七區同時集會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/30/142310_24c8e361b664019ceb44fc4a7f538cd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F142310_24c8e361b664019ceb44fc4a7f538cd2.png&h=0943bb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但衍生出嚟嘅一個問題係，分開七區集會緊會唔會變成<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">某啲區特別少人</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n預計大埔、沙田、金鐘最多人；<span style=\"color: red;\">屯門，荃灣，黃大仙應該最少</span>；旺角就覺得太危險同埋冇乜地方俾人集合，所以難以預計<br />\n<br />\n七區集會換言之警力都會分散左～大家集思廣益下其實我哋有乜嘢策略？需唔需要集合一啲人定係真係分到七個區咁散？一個區有事其他區點樣支援？"},{"pid":"b1090305473f115f8bf2ab7b10c639089ba8ac31","tid":1385622,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"補充集會地點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELAbKrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELAbKrV.png&h=42363429&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}